HEADWORD: Explainable
<hw>Ex*plain"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>explainabilis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Capable of being explained or made
plain to the understanding; capable of being interpreted.</def>
<rj><au>Sir. T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> explicable.</syn>
